text:
Great experience. The place looks just like the photos, but has an even cozier more welcoming feel to it.

I loved the fresh water carafes and set of plush robes in every room : )

Welcome bottle of wine was very much appreciated after a day of travel and Ashley was kind enough to allow us a late check out to accommodate our later departing flight.

I would absolutely stay here again!
title: Modern, Urban Oasis for 8 SoCo/SoFi
